These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, tea, iced-tea, soy-milk
Pet: chinchilla, hamster, hedgehog, turtle
1. Pet:turtle is on the left of Beverage:iced-tea##1
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left of Pet:hamster##1
3. Beverage:soy-milk is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:hedgehog is on the left or right of Pet:turtle##3
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | tea | soy-milk | iced-tea |
| Pet        | chinchilla | hamster   | turtle | hedgehog    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: adventure, satire, drama, horror
Nationality: malaysian, japanese, indonesian, dutch
1. Movie-Genre:satire is on the left of Movie-Genre:horror##1
2. Nationality:malaysian is on the left of Nationality:indonesian##1
3. Nationality:indonesian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:malaysian == Movie-Genre:adventure##1
5. Nationality:japanese is on the right of Nationality:indonesian##1
6. Nationality:malaysian == Movie-Genre:adventure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | adventure  | satire  | horror |
| Nationality   | dutch    | malaysian | indonesian | japanese    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: apricot, spinach, artichoke, garlic
Movie-Genre: drama, horror, satire, mystery
1. Food:garlic is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:mystery##3
2. Food:artichoke is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left or right of Food:spinach##3
4. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the right of Movie-Genre:satire##1
5. Movie-Genre:drama is in an odd position##4
6. Food:spinach is on the right of Food:artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | garlic | artichoke | spinach    | apricot      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire        | mystery     | drama | horror |

