.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: card-games, singing, traveling, magic-tricks
Music-Genre: electronic, trance, punk, hip-hop
1. Hobby:singing is between Music-Genre:electronic and Music-Genre:hip-hop##2
2. Hobby:magic-tricks is on the left of Hobby:card-games##1
3. Music-Genre:punk is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:trance is on the left of Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
5. Music-Genre:trance is on the right of Hobby:card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | card-games | singing | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | electronic   | trance    | hip-hop  |

