.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: dubstep, soul, disco, house
Nationality: british, malaysian, polish, german
1. Music-Genre:disco is on the right of Nationality:german##1
2. Nationality:malaysian == Music-Genre:house##1
3. Nationality:polish is on the right of Music-Genre:dubstep##1
4. Music-Genre:soul is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:disco is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:british is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | dubstep    | disco   | house       |
| Nationality   | british | german | polish | malaysian |

