.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, 7up, tea, fanta
Music-Genre: reggae, classical, country, indie
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate == Music-Genre:indie##1
2. Music-Genre:reggae is on the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is between Music-Genre:reggae and Beverage:tea##2
4. Beverage:hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:indie is on the left or right of Music-Genre:reggae##3
6. Beverage:7up is on the left or right of Music-Genre:classical##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up       | tea   | hot-chocolate | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | country | classical | indie        | reggae    |

