.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: sprite, coffee, hot-chocolate, lemonade
Food: plum, radish, carrot, orange
1. Food:radish is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Beverage:sprite##3
3. Beverage:lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:carrot is on the left of Food:orange##1
5. Food:orange is on the right of Beverage:sprite##1
6. Food:carrot is in an even position##4
7. Food:plum == Beverage:coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | sprite    | hot-chocolate       | coffee |
| Food       | radish  | carrot | orange | plum  |

